x86: mm: use ARCH_HAS_DEBUG_WX instead of arch defined

Extract DEBUG_WX to mm/Kconfig.debug for shared use.  Change to use
ARCH_HAS_DEBUG_WX instead of DEBUG_WX defined by arch port.

